overview.overview: Compass is a free interactive tool for querying, optimizing, and analyzing your MongoDB data. Get key insights, drag and drop to build pipelines, and more.

childMarkdownRemark.html: 在Compass中轻松处理您的数据，Compass是由MongoDB构建的GUI。Compass 在单个集中式界面中提供从模式分析到索引优化再到聚合管道的所有内容。
